- The `NewChannel` function creates a new instance of `Channel`, specifying its initial capacity.
- The `Add` method allows producers to add items to the channel.
- The `Take` method allows consumers to remove items from the channel. It blocks until there's something available or until all consumers have finished consuming items (if the channel is full).
- The `consume` method checks if there are any consumers still waiting before proceeding.

